Objective: Develop a billing system that can manage project-related invoices, customer data, billing schedules, and payment tracking.

Key Features:

Customer Management: Maintain customer master data.

Project Management: Link projects to customers and track project-specific details.

Billing Processes: Generate invoices, handle recurring billing, and manage billing adjustments.

Payment Reconciliation: Monitor invoice statuses, payment receipts, and dunning processes.

Reporting: Create standard and ad-hoc reports for analysis.
